      "content": "Focus on immaculate grooming; your hair should be neatly styled, and your nails perfectly manicured. Wear tailored, high-quality clothing in conservative colors like navy or charcoal to project seriousness. Maintain impeccable posture—sitting or standing tall immediately signals confidence and authority. These small details communicate that you respect the gravity of the meeting and yourself.",
